Package: globalPM25
Title: Query real-time local air pollute PM2.5 level near you, at any city around the world or a user-defined geographical boundary
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Jinhua", "Li", email = "jinhua.li000@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The real-time data soruce is coming from \url{aqicn.org}. First, Request your personal API token from \url{http://aqicn.org/data-platform/token/#/}. Set your personal token. Then you can query PM2.5 level near you, at any city or a list of cities worldwide, in any city area, or within a geographical boundary. 
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2)
Imports: jsonlite, tibble, dplyr, utils
Suggests: testthat
License: GPL(>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
